<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#fff" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <table border="0" cellspacing="20" align="center"
        style="max-width: 602px; width:100%; background: #fff; border: solid 1rem #eee; color: #404040; padding: 2rem;">
        <tr>
            <td valign="middle" style="padding-bottom: 1rem;">
                <img src="https://i.ibb.co/92134y6/logo-dark.png" alt="LOGO"
                    style="width: 2rem; height: 2rem; display: inline-block;             vertical-align: middle;">
                <h1 style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 1.4rem;">
                    Footprint
                </h1>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <h2 style="color:#505050; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
                    Ciao {{username}}!
                </h2>
                <p style="color:#505050; margin:0; font-size: 1rem; padding-top: .5rem; padding-bottom: 1rem;">
                    Ci risulta che stai cercando di cambiare la password del tuo account. Ti baster√† riportare il codice
                    sottostante nell'applicazione.
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td align="center" valign="middle"
                style="width: 100%; text-align: center; user-select: all;font-size: 1.5rem;  border: solid 2px #808080; border-left: none; border-right: none; padding: 5px 0">
                <strong style="color: #404040">{{token}}</strong>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
